file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - CHAPTER 12-21-15-03 - MAIN DOOR - SERVICING

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL MAIN DOOR - SERVICING EFFECTIVITY: ALL 1. General A. The procedure for the lubrication of the Main Door is given in AMM TASK 52-11-00-600-801- A/300 (airstairs main door) or AMM TASK 52-18-00-600-801-A/300 (side-hinged main door).
